in your opinion what is a better company blizzard or ea in my opinion blizzard is the better company on the offline games front i've primarily played the sims series from ea which is really addicting and was innovative and diablo diablo from blizzard which were also addicting if not quite as innovative the games to me are about equally enjoyable comparing online games however blizzard shines even disregarding the fact that wow is as popular as it is ea has had ultima online and the sims online and soon warhammer online since and has done basically nothing with it although i still pay for my account there it is primarily for sentimental reasons blizzard did a much better job of creating a formula that works keeping players interested balancing classes having a storyline and providing a rewarding end game experience lastly and this is hearsay and board gossip not personal experience but ea seems to have a history of overworking their employees and not treating them very well whereas i've heard good things about working for blizzard and i wouldn't be surprised if this contributes to the quality of the games they produce Pok__mon FireRed and LeafGreen Pok__mon Emerald Pok__mon (video games) Elite Four Pok__mon Ruby and Sapphire Onix Pok__mon Pok__mon Gold and Silver Latios Pok__mon Colosseum Latias Raichu Pok__mon Red and Blue Pok__mon (anime) Mewtwo Rayquaza Game Freak Charizard Chansey Pok__mon Adventures Jynx (Pok__mon) Pikachu Altaria Indigo Plateau Charmander Missingno. Sevii Islands Pok__mon Abilities Togepi Misty (Pok__mon) Gengar Birthday Ho-Oh Blastoise Cerulean City Pok__mon Trading Card Game Mightyena Glitch City Wailmer Pok__mon Gym Blue (Pok__mon) Gemstone Red (Pok__mon) Snorlax Viridian City Hoenn Page Falkenberg Pok__mon Stadium Magneton Pok__mon Trainer Farfetch'd Deoxys Voltorb Ralts Gardevoir Groudon Team Rocket Pinsir Raticate Shiny Pok__mon Pok__mon XD: Gale of Darkness Rhyhorn Charmeleon Entei (Pok__mon) Primeape Smeargle Chaos Emerald Zapdos Torkoa